{
  "texts": [
    "As operational artificial intelligence develops, the requirement of proper application becomes first priority.",
    "Prompt engineering is also important as it helps models to avoid biased, harmful, or misleading responses via cautious supervision.",
    "This is a shared responsibility among engineers, domain experts, and ethical leaders all across teams.",
    "Future success of artificial intelligence depends on our interactions with the models as much as on their performance.",
    "The language of our modern day is prompt engineering, so businesses must interact with it deliberately, ethically, and fluently."
  ]
}